Dracona walks up to Nemesis Enforcer.. "what happened to everyone? she said
as she looked around... "what happened? this seems familiar.....everyone
seems to have disappeared!..." she blinked her eyes.....her eye scar where
Dinobot shot her shining in the light..... "what are my orders temporary
leader!?" she says to Nemesis.....
